### 1. List sightings for bird 1 (Great Kiskadee)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/birds/1/sightings

###

### 2. List sightings for bird 3 (Black-bellied Whistling-Duck)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/birds/3/sightings

###

### 3. List sightings for bird 999 (not found)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/birds/999/sightings

###

### 4. Get sighting by ID
GET http://localhost:8787/api/sightings/1

###

### 5. Get sighting not found
GET http://localhost:8787/api/sightings/999

###

### 6. Create sighting for bird 2 — valid
POST http://localhost:8787/api/birds/2/sightings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Thicket survey",
  "description": "Heard calling from dense brush near creek.",
  "status": "logged"
}

###

### 7. Create sighting — missing title (422)
POST http://localhost:8787/api/birds/1/sightings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "No title here"
}

###

### 8. Create sighting — invalid status (422)
POST http://localhost:8787/api/birds/1/sightings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bad status test",
  "status": "in-progress"
}

###

### 9. Create sighting — status and description omitted (defaults applied)
POST http://localhost:8787/api/birds/2/sightings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Quick flyover"
}

###

### 10. Patch sighting 1 — update status
PATCH http://localhost:8787/api/sightings/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "logged"
}

###

### 11. Patch sighting — empty body (422)
PATCH http://localhost:8787/api/sightings/1
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### 12. Patch sighting — invalid status (422)
PATCH http://localhost:8787/api/sightings/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "done"
}

###

### 13. Delete sighting 2
DELETE http://localhost:8787/api/sightings/2

###

### 14. Delete again — not found (404)
DELETE http://localhost:8787/api/sightings/2

###

### 15. List bird 1 sightings after delete — count drops to 1
GET http://localhost:8787/api/birds/1/sightings

###

### 16. Delete a bird — cascade should remove its sightings
DELETE http://localhost:8787/api/birds/1

###

### 17. Confirm no sightings orphaned — should return empty collection
GET http://localhost:8787/api/birds/1/sightings